title: The Fellowship of the Ring of Free Trade - by St01en Collective (2002)
description:
Peter Jackson's blockbuster motion picture version of J.R.R. Tolkien epic The Lord of the Rings is reinterpreted through the use of subtitles to bring the narrative into the 21st century. The story is transformed from the archetypal struggle between good and evil into a pointed commentary on the "impending crisis of capitalist modernity". 

FAIR USE NOTICE: This critical and transformative remix video has been uploaded here for noncommercial educational and archival purposes. As such we believe it constitutes a fair use of any copyrighted material as provided for in section 107 of the US copyright law.
